# thoth_governance_settings

Manages compliance profile, risk policy, secret broker controls, and model router policy.

Use `compliance_profile` for a preset baseline and `regulatory_regimes` for explicit obligations.
When `regulatory_regimes` is omitted, GovAPI falls back to profile defaults and then `soc2`.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_governance_settings" "tenant_policy" {
  compliance_profile = "soc2"
  regulatory_regimes = ["soc2", "sec_cftc"]
  shadow_low         = "allow"
  shadow_medium      = "step_up"
  shadow_high        = "block"
  shadow_critical    = "block"

  model_router_enabled          = true
  model_router_default_provider = "openai"
  model_router_default_model    = "gpt-4o-mini"
}
```
